# No cross-project references

- Do not mention other repositories, apps, design kits, or sibling folders in source code or comments.
- Schema and model comments describe the Firestore/RTDB contract only (collection paths, field names).
- Do not add comments like “mirrors X”, “from Y kit”, or “like Z product”.
